We will look more closely in the next several chapters at the
cultures of all these regions, as they entered the modern era.
Although the people of each continent and region developed
different traditions and customs, their agriculturally-based
cultures shared a lot of similarities and their civilizations were
all comparably advanced at the beginning of our survey. with
that introduction, let’s begin.

